 appeal to a poorer, older, less prepared element.', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:25:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "86167c73b112", "answer_pdf_sha1": "df3e6e4e372c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110130", "c": "409", "s": "0316", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "綜合法政知識與英文(包括中華民國憲法、法學緒論、兩岸關係、英文)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、移民行政人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格者取得法官遴選資格考...", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "investigation", "civil_category": "法律實務組"}'::jsonb, NULL),
